data.description: A must see! Great starter home! This lovely 2-level rancher sits on 3/4 acres and boasts 5 bedrooms, 3 full baths,  and a bonus room for either an extra living room off the kitchen to entertain  or another dining room . The main level is light-filled and features a sizeable living room , a dedicated dining area, an updated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, a master bedroom  with a totally redone master bath and large walk in closet, 2 additional bedrooms, and a full hall bath, in addition to  the trex deck off the kitchen overlooking the incredible backyard. The finished lower level is open concept with a large 5th bedroom and a bonus room. Freshly painted , and fully carpeted.  Extended driveway with plentiful parking. Level lot. Feels like a private retreat, but offers quick access to shopping, dining, recreation, and commuter routes. Don't miss you chance to own this oasis! Conveniently located near Rt. 22, Rt. 40 & I95 make an offer.
